Build a production-quality local web application: a Kubernetes/OpenShift log explorer designed for stable, predictable debugging using a snapshot + refresh model (NO live streaming by default).

The goal is to eliminate UI chaos while preserving full log fidelity and context.

---

🧱 Tech Stack (STRICT)

Frontend

- React (Vite)
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS
- shadcn/ui
- Zustand (state management)
- react-window (virtualized rendering)

Backend

